msgid ""
"This example demonstrates how to read ADC values and switch status from "
"the Chain Switch sensor and display them on screen. It registers "
"open/close trigger callbacks and updates the status label when the switch"
" state changes."
msgstr ""
"本示例演示如何从 Chain Switch 传感器读取 ADC 值和开关状态并显示在屏幕上。它注册打开/关闭触发回调，并在开关状态变化时更新状态标签。"

